I was stuck on a crappy PvP server.  I wanted to move, but didn't want to give up my epic, other gear I'd spent 3 years getting.  So...  I moved to Stormhammer (Legends).  Great!  But it's just a bit better than a normal blue server and it's way overpriced....<br>
<br>
So they open up Maelin Starpyre!  Cool, I can move and not pay the Legends fees!  Wait, hold on, you can't move to Maelin Starpyre from Stormhammer, we want your Legends money!<br>
<br>
Ok, no problem, I'll move back to Tallon Zek, took me 2 hours to move to Legends, moving back to my PvP server shouldn't be too bad.  Three weeks go by.  The deadline for moving to Maelin Starpyre passes, THEN they move my character.  Hmm...  sounds fishy.<br>
<br>
So I move him back to Stormhammer, which they say they are doing me a &quot;favor&quot; because it's normally 30 days before they move you back.  Pfffttt..<br>
<br>
I see another new server is opening up!  Oh wait, no transfers to this server.<br>
